messages.message:
Hi team,
Whenever i try to download any DL model trained on instabase (~400Mb)  i get this bad gateway error.

I guess something is timing out before File service is able to serve the model? I see this on dogfood, ib.com (http://ib.com) and in the HSBC environment.

Customers are going to encounter this pretty quickly as they try to export models to move them between different environments (as I am now doing).
